::Striker::

Striker smiles, walking out of the Ark and guiding Spears along. The feel of 
her arm against his excited him, more than he thought a touch could. His 
smile deepens, looking at her.

"There's a nice place a little ways from here," Striker says to Spears, "If 
it hasn't been destroyed by attacks yet."
